
Steps to Do :

1. First Create the project (Xunit) 
2. Class will be created having method called Unittest1 ( Rename this based on what we need )
3. Then add the reference to the project that you are going to test from this project
  { command : dotnet add ./ReportGeneratorTests/ReportGeneratorTests.csproj reference ./PracticeDesignPatterns/PracticeDesignPatterns.csproj 
     TestProjectName -> Testclass ->  ./ReportGeneratorTests/ReportGeneratorTests.csproj
     TargetProject -> Targetclass ->   ./PracticeDesignPatterns/PracticeDesignPatterns.csproj 

  Syntax =>  dotnet add ./{TestProject}/{TestClass} .csproj   reference   ./{TargetProj}/{TargetClass} .csproj
 
